text: Faizal Yusof (1979 - 1 January 2011) was a Malaysian actor. He acted in the popular television series Tiramisu and Manjalara. He died from heart failure, and was buried in the Batu Mudu Muslim Cemetery in Kuala Lumpur. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Malaysian actors Category:Television actors Category:People from Kuala Lumpur
